ealth challenges. </li> </ul> </div> </div> <div class="badges__ctaBtn"> <a class="btn" href="/courses/course-guides/graduate-diploma-of-public-health-course-guide" title="Download course guide | Torrens University">Download course guide</a> <a class="btn-link" href="https://apply.torrens.edu.au/" title="Start online application | Torrens University">Start online application</a> </div> </div>',
