 </li> <li>Employ a diverse range of communication strategies to achieve objectives and influence stakeholders <br/> </li> </ul> </div> </div> <div class="badges__ctaBtn"> <a class="btn" href="https://ducere.education/course/graduate-certificate-of-applied-business/" title="Download course guide | Torrens University">Download course guide</a> <a class="btn-link" href="https://courses.ducere.education/tua-enrolment-form" title="Start online application | Torrens University">Start online application</a> </div> </div>',
