ation across global teams and communities.</li> <li>Practice critical and creative thinking to define and solve problems through design projects.</li> </ul> </div> </div> <div class="component badges"> <div class="component-content"><div class="badges__item"> <div class="badges__img"> </div> <div class="badges__text"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"> Adobe affiliation benefits </p> <p> You''ll receive a free Adobe Creative Cloud Pro licence for the entire time you''re studying Design with us. </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="badges__ctaBtn"> <a class="btn" href="/courses/course-guides/graduate-certificate-of-design" title="Download course guide | Torrens University">Download course guide</a> <a class="btn-link" href="https://apply.torrens.edu.au/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" title="Start online application | Torrens University Australia">Start online application</a> </div> </div>',
