    course_description = '<div class="course-overview__left" data-coursename="Diploma of Design" data-coursetype="Undergraduate" data-studenttypes="Domestic, International" id="course-data"> <div class="component rich-text"> <div class="component-content"> <p style="font-weight: bold;">What is a Diploma of Design?</p> This Diploma of Design is your all-access pass, allowing you to find your niche in the world of professional design. In just one year, you''ll build a solid foundation of the design principles that guide our industry, working alongside other creative rebels and supported by industry pros. This course is the perfect way to kickstart a career. <div class="expand-text"> <p>In dynamic studios and hands-on environments, you’ll collaborate, tackle and work on real design briefs. Designed for everyone – whether you’re new to the game or already have some design chops – the Diploma of Design serves up a broad taste of the industry. With a plethora of electives, you’ll be able to deep dive into a chosen area and get a taste of Branded Fashion Design, Fashion Marketing and Enterprise, Communication Design, Interior Design or even Architectural Technology. Not sure what you’d choose? We’ve got you covered with our pick and mix option. Tailored specifically for direct entry, this diploma gives you full credit into a bachelor’s degree. </p> </div> <p><a class="btn-tertiary jsToggleExpand" data-less="Less" data-more="More" href="#">More</a> </p> </div> </div> <div class="component bullet-list"> <div class="component-content"> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Learning outcomes</p> <ul> <li>Develop creative confidence in a specialist field of your choice.</li> <li>Learn to create real design solutions to real problems.</li> <li>Learn to examine, question and evolve ideas in the same way professionals do in the industry.</li> <li>Learn how to communicate your design ideas to different audiences.</li> <li>Understand how design shapes the world around us.</li> <li>Understand the impacts of and advocate for ethical design practices.</li> </ul> </div> </div> <div class="component badges"> <div class="component-content"><div class="badges__item"> <div class="badges__img"> </div> <div class="badges__text"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"> Free Adobe Creative Cloud Pro licence </p> <p> You''ll receive a free Adobe Creative Cloud Pro licence for the entire time you''re studying Design with us and for six months post graduation. </p> </div> </div> <div class="badges__item"> <div class="badges__img"> </div> <div class="badges__text"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"> Vogue Australia partnership </p> <p> We’ve partnered with industry leaders including Vogue Australia, to offer you internship, mentoring and scholarship opportunities. </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="badges__ctaBtn"> <a class="btn" href="/courses/course-guides/diploma-of-design-course-guide" title="Download course guide | Torrens University">Download course guide</a> <a class="btn-link" href="https://apply.torrens.edu.au/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" title="Start online application | Torrens University">Start online application</a> </div> </div>',
