ence a range of architectural design proposals. </li> <li>Evaluate human needs and the impact of new architectural artefacts for optimal spatial planning. </li> <li>Develop your knowledge of electrical, mechanical, plumbing and structural engineering services to develop integrated building solutions.</li> <li>Undertake 120 hours of experience by completing an internship or working on a live brief.</li> </ul> </div> </div> <div class="badges__ctaBtn"> <a class="btn" href="/courses/course-guides/bachelor-of-architectural-technology-course-guide" title="Download course guide | Torrens University">Download course guide</a> <a class="btn-link" href="https://apply.torrens.edu.au/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" title="Start online application | Torrens University">Start online application</a> </div> </div>',
