 student membership. ACS is the largest professional association for Australia''s tech sector with members from across business, government and education. </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="badges__ctaBtn"> <a class="btn" href="/courses/course-guides/master-of-software-engineering-artificial-intelligence-course-guide" title="Download course guide | Torrens University">Download course guide</a> <a class="btn-link" href="https://apply.torrens.edu.au/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" title="Start online application | Torrens University">Start online application</a> </div> </div>',
