ges__text"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"> IIBA member </p> <p> Our Business Analytics programs are endorsed by the International Institute of Business Analysis (IIBA). Full-time, enrolled students can apply for a 12-month student membership. </p> </div> </div> <div class="badges__item"> <div class="badges__img"> </div> <div class="badges__text"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"> EFMD member </p> <p> The European Foundation for Management Development (EFMD) is dedicated to management development. Our membership demonstrates our commitment to ensuring our programs provide the highest quality, aligned education. </p> </div> </div> <div class="badges__item"> <div class="badges__img"> </div> <div class="badges__text"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"> Complimentary ACS membership </p> <p> Students studying Business Analytics courses at Torrens University are eligible for a complimentary ACS student membership. ACS is the largest professional association for Australia''s tech sector with members from across business, government and education. </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="badges__ctaBtn"> <a class="btn" href="/courses/course-guides/graduate-certificate-of-analytics-course-guide" title="Download course guide | Torrens University">Download course guide</a> <a class="btn-link" href="https://apply.torrens.edu.au/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" title="Start Online Application | Torrens University">Start online application</a> </div> </div>',
