dges"> <div class="component-content"><div class="badges__item"> <div class="badges__img">  </div> <div class="badges__text"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"> AWS Certified Cloud Practitioner </p> <p> Our Microservices Architecture subject is aligned to meet the knowledge requirements of the AWS Certified Cloud Practitioner certification. </p> </div> </div> <div class="badges__item"> <div class="badges__img"> </div> <div class="badges__text"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"> Cisco Networking Academy Partner </p> <p> As a partner, students can access additional learning materials and work towards Cisco certification-aligned pathways. </p> </div> </div> <div class="badges__item"> <div class="badges__img"> </div> <div class="badges__text"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"> Complimentary ACS membership </p> <p> Students studying Business Information Systems courses at Torrens University are eligible for a complimentary ACS student membership. ACS is the largest professional association for Australia''s tech sector with members from across business, government and education. </p> </div> </div> <div class="badges__item"> <div class="badges__img"> </div> <div class="badges__text"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"> EFMD member </p> <p> The European Foundation for Management Development (EFMD) is dedicated to management development. Our membership demonstrates our commitment to ensuring our programs provide the highest quality, aligned education. </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="badges__ctaBtn"> <a class="btn" href="/courses/course-guides/graduate-diploma-of-business-information-systems-course-guide" title="Download course guide | Torrens University">Download course guide</a> <a class="btn-link" href="https://apply.torrens.edu.au" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" title="Start online application | Torrens University Australia">Start online application</a> </div> </div>',
