ts. </li> <li>Understand and apply research methodologies in a variety of sport management contexts. </li> <li>Creatively solve complex problems unique to sport management, including developing strategies to assist in sporting success.</li> </ul> </div> </div> <div class="component badges"> <div class="component-content"><div class="badges__item"> <div class="badges__img"> </div> <div class="badges__text"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"> EFMD member </p> <p> The European Foundation for Management Development (EFMD) is dedicated to management development. Our membership demonstrates our commitment to ensuring our programs provide the highest quality, aligned education. </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="badges__ctaBtn"> <a class="btn" href="/courses/course-guides/graduate-certificate-of-sport-management-course-guide" title="Download course guide | Torrens University">Download course guide</a> <a class="btn-link" href="https://apply.torrens.edu.au/" title="Start online application | Torrens University">Start online application</a> </div> </div>',
