oherent communication skills to report, present, publish and disseminate research data and findings to peers and the community. </li> <li>Exhibit autonomy, authoritative judgement and leadership in workplace research and advanced professional practice. </li> </ul> </div> </div> <div class="badges__ctaBtn"> <a class="btn" href="/courses/course-guides/professional-doctorate-applied-research-course-guide" title="Download course guide | Torrens University">Download course guide</a> <a class="btn-link" href="https://apply.torrens.edu.au/" title="Start online application | Torrens University">Start online application</a> </div> </div>',
