    course_description = '<div class="course-overview__left" data-coursename="Master of Business Administration (On Demand)" data-coursetype="Postgraduate" data-studenttypes="Domestic, International (offshore)" id="course-data"> <div class="component rich-text"> <div class="component-content"> <p style="font-weight: bold;">What is an MBA (On Demand)?</p> An MBA builds the technical, creative and leadership skills needed to make effective business decisions and lead dynamic organisations in a global context. Consisting of six core and six elective subjects, you can tailor the course to your career goals and progress on your terms. You can also choose to enter or exit with a Graduate Certificate of Business Administration (On Demand) or Graduate Diploma of Business Administration (On Demand). <div class="expand-text"> <p>This MBA (On Demand) is one of the most accessible and future-focused MBAs, now powered by our MBA Flex model. With no scheduled classes and 24/7 access to your learning materials, you have the freedom to design a study journey that truly fits your life. Flex puts you in control: choose from 10 intakes a year, finish a subject in as little as 4 weeks or take up to 12, with fast 48-hour marking so your momentum never slows.</p> </div> <p><a class="btn-tertiary jsToggleExpand" data-less="Less" data-more="More" href="#">More</a> </p> </div> </div> <div class="component bullet-list"> <div class="component-content"> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Learning outcomes</p> <ul> <li>Apply advanced business principles to solve complex problems. </li> <li>Lead teams and individuals in ethical decision-making.</li> <li>Systematically evaluate business risk and communicate findings to a broader audience.</li> <li>Master industry-standard business software to effectively analyse data.</li> </ul> </div> </div> <div class="component badges"> <div class="component-content"><div class="badges__item"> <div class="badges__img">  </div> <div class="badges__text"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"> Top 10 globally </p> <p> </p><p>Our MBA (On Demand) is a flexible, world-class program, ranked Top 10 globally by CEO Magazine.</p> <p></p> </div> </div> <div class="badges__item"> <div class="badges__img"> </div> <div class="badges__text"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"> Top-ranked MBA school </p> <p> Our MBA program was ranked Tier-1 by CEO Magazine in 2025, putting it among the world''s best. </p> </div> </div> <div class="badges__item"> <div class="badges__img"> </div> <div class="badges__text"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"> EFMD member </p> <p> The European Foundation for Management Development (EFMD) is dedicated to management development. Our membership demonstrates our commitment to ensuring our programs provide the highest quality, aligned education. </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="badges__ctaBtn"> <a class="btn" href="/courses/course-guides/master-of-business-administration-mba-on-demand-course-guide" title="Download course guide | Torrens University">Download course guide</a> <a class="btn-link" href="https://apply.torrens.edu.au/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" title="Start Online Application | Torrens University">Start online application</a> </div> </div>',
