nt to business and social challenges.</li> </ul> </div> </div> <div class="component badges"> <div class="component-content"><div class="badges__item"> <div class="badges__img"> </div> <div class="badges__text"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"> IIBA member </p> <p> Our Business Analytics programs are endorsed by the International Institute of Business Analysis (IIBA). Full-time, enrolled students can apply for a 12-month student membership. </p> </div> </div> <div class="badges__item"> <div class="badges__img"> </div> <div class="badges__text"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"> ECBA exam preparation </p> <p> Our Business Analytics programs are structured to help prepare students to sit the International Institute of Business Analysis'' Entry Certificate in Business Analysis exam. </p> </div> </div> <div class="badges__item"> <div class="badges__img"> </div> <div class="badges__text"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"> Tableau''s Desktop Specialist </p> <p> </p><p>Our Visual Analytics and Storytelling subject is aligned to meet the knowledge requirements of the Certified Tableau Desktop Foundations certification.</p> <p></p> </div> </div> <div class="badges__item"> <div class="badges__img"> </div> <div class="badges__text"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"> SAS® Certified Specialist: Machine Learning </p> <p> </p><p>Our Applied Optimisation in Business subject is structured to advance your data analysis skills, leveraging SAS® software and machine learning techniques.</p> <p></p> </div> </div> <div class="badges__item"> <div class="badges__img"> </div> <div class="badges__text"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"> EFMD member </p> <p> The European Foundation for Management Development (EFMD) is dedicated to management development. Our membership demonstrates our commitment to ensuring our programs provide the highest quality, aligned education. </p> </div> </div> <div class="badges__item"> <div class="badges__img"> </div> <div class="badges__text"> <p style="font-weight: bold;"> Complimentary ACS membership </p> <p> Students studying Business Analytics courses at Torrens University are eligible for a complimentary ACS student membership. ACS is the largest professional association for Australia''s tech sector with members from across business, government and education. </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="badges__ctaBtn"> <a class="btn" href="/courses/course-guides/graduate-diploma-of-business-analytics-course-guide" title="Download course guide | Torrens University">Download course guide</a> <a class="btn-link" href="https://apply.torrens.edu.au" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" title="Start online application | Torrens University Australia">Start online application</a> </div> </div>',
